CBlog is a blog engine written in C

it is licensed under the new BSD license.
it features : 
	- clearsilver template engine,
	- markdown text format for posts using Natacha's markdown parser (embeded see markdown.{c,h})
	- tags support,
	- no SQL engine,
	- plain text format

it uses software developped by iMil : see tools.h and tools.c	
